    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "FTR, it looks like there is a race happening between GC shutting down the server and it being explicitly shut down by the app (from a separate thread from the main thread). One fix is to protect the internal destroy server function from the race. But I'm still not sure why GC is running on the ruby server while it's still being shut down (ref to it is still alive) - more investigation needed to find that out."
